        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-365c8d44-dd1f-43f5-8736-6ca4b771f111">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-365c8d44-dd1f-43f5-8736-6ca4b771f111">
                 Mr. Mander 
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-365c8d44-dd1f-43f5-8736-6ca4b771f111" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1941-04-22/debates/58ff96cb-e300-48ce-ab52-70f7c8c4e585/Spain(BritishLoan)#contribution-365c8d44-dd1f-43f5-8736-6ca4b771f111">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Minister of Economic Warfare what action he is taking to prevent the export of large quantities of iron ore from Bilbao to Germany; and whether this question was taken into consideration when the recent loan of £2,500,000 by Great Britain to Spain was made?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-365c8d44-dd1f-43f5-8736-6ca4b771f111" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1941-04-22/debates/58ff96cb-e300-48ce-ab52-70f7c8c4e585/Spain(BritishLoan)#contribution-365c8d44-dd1f-43f5-8736-6ca4b771f111">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-f96ac7b1-c726-4a17-9264-9b3c16e4c7ca">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-f96ac7b1-c726-4a17-9264-9b3c16e4c7ca">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-f96ac7b1-c726-4a17-9264-9b3c16e4c7ca">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-f96ac7b1-c726-4a17-9264-9b3c16e4c7ca">
                Mr. Dalton
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-f96ac7b1-c726-4a17-9264-9b3c16e4c7ca" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1941-04-22/debates/58ff96cb-e300-48ce-ab52-70f7c8c4e585/Spain(BritishLoan)#contribution-f96ac7b1-c726-4a17-9264-9b3c16e4c7ca">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">So far as I am aware, no export of large quantities of iron ore from Bilbao to Germany is taking place. I shall, however, be very glad to receive any information which my hon. Friend may have on the subject. All relevant considerations were borne in mind when the recent loan agreement was negotiated.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f96ac7b1-c726-4a17-9264-9b3c16e4c7ca" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1941-04-22/debates/58ff96cb-e300-48ce-ab52-70f7c8c4e585/Spain(BritishLoan)#contribution-f96ac7b1-c726-4a17-9264-9b3c16e4c7ca">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-2f3efd59-3466-4f51-b670-89c9e2ac6bca">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-2f3efd59-3466-4f51-b670-89c9e2ac6bca">
